BOT-2: Create a script and docker container that runs PSST and outputs a matrix

Address privacy in readme
body: Could you say a little bit more about data security and patient privacy in the readme?  This is a big concern and it's only very briefly addressed here.

title: Sean, have you seen this repo?
description
body: A robotic encapsulation of a variant calling robot that can return de-identified results.
